<div id=mido>
<h1>讪</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">shàn</span><span class=alesi>(shan4)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 讪 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 讪</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/abuse" style="color:black;">abuse</a>, <a href="/dictionary/slander" style="color:black;">slander</a>; <a href="/dictionary/vilify" style="color:black;">vilify</a>; ridicule</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 5<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 5 strokes: <a href="/character/他" title="ta1: other, another; he, she, it">他</a>, <a href="/character/们" title="men: adjunct pronoun indicate plural">们</a>, <a href="/character/出" title="chu1: go out, send out; stand; produce">出</a>, <a href="/character/可" title="ke3: may, can, -able; possibly">可</a>, <a href="/character/对" title="dui4: correct, right; facing, opposed">对</a>, <a href="/character/生" title="sheng1: life, living, lifetime; birth">生</a>, <a href="/character/发" title="fa1: issue, dispatch, send out; hair">发</a>, <a href="/character/用" title="yong4: use, employ, apply, operate; use">用</a>, <a href="/character/去" title="qu4: go away, leave, depart">去</a>, <a href="/character/主" title="zhu3: master, chief owner; host; lord">主</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/言" title="Kangxi radical 149">言</a>&nbsp;149.3</p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 3679</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 3556</p><p><b>Traditional variant:</b> <a href="/character/訕">訕</a></p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/搭讪" title="da1 shan4">搭讪</a>, <a href="/dictionary/答讪" title="da1 shan4">答讪</a>, <a href="/dictionary/讪笑" title="shan4 xiao4">讪笑</a>, <a href="/dictionary/讪脸" title="shan4 lian3">讪脸</a>, <a href="/dictionary/讪讪" title="shan4 shan4">讪讪</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">訕|讪[<span style="color:#000099;">shàn</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- to mock<br>- to ridicule<br>- to slander<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><h2>Details</h2><p><b>Unicode code point:</b> U+8BAA</p></div>

